25:45.858 --> 25:47.761
Because life can be challenging, can't it?

25:47.781 --> 25:50.185
You know, life can have its ups and downs.

25:50.886 --> 26:05.588
But when you gather weekly in church, when you are known and know others, when the challenges come, the canes are placed around you.

26:08.793 --> 26:11.858
You will be supported, encouraged and spurred on.

26:13.954 --> 26:20.983
You know, over 19, the 19 years that we've led at life in our church, or life living churches have been existed.

26:22.605 --> 26:27.411
We've had people come to us, yes, not many, but a few, and say, we don't feel supported.

26:29.233 --> 26:31.376
