26:32.437 --> 26:39.186
But pretty much every time when we've dug a little deeper, they're not regularly at church, and they're not part of a life group.

26:41.762 --> 26:46.227
And so, you know, we obviously look at ways in which we can support them once we know.

26:48.509 --> 26:51.553
