27:38.530 --> 27:39.431
and who don't know others.

27:41.734 --> 27:43.676
In gathering weekly, we get to build friendships.

27:45.498 --> 27:47.700
Gathering weekly anchors us in a church family.

27:48.361 --> 27:52.786
We are fed by the scriptures, watered by the Holy Spirit, and supported by the church family.

27:54.728 --> 28:00.435
