28:19.133 --> 28:21.115
Make hay where the sun shines.

28:23.958 --> 28:25.520
When we can, let's make hay.

28:25.920 --> 28:26.881
Let's make friends.

28:27.241 --> 28:31.566
Let's anchor ourselves for when the winds come and the storms come.

28:32.947 --> 28:35.570
The canes will be in place that will hold us firm.

28:39.298 --> 28:40.039
But it's a choice.

28:41.501 --> 28:43.323
It's a choice at the start of 2026.

