29:08.354 --> 29:17.066
Round gathering weekly helps us to remove the weeds from our life and the pollution from our lives.

29:18.468 --> 29:27.181
Then we will no longer be infants tossed back and forth by the waves and blown here and there by every wind of teaching and by the cunning craftiness of people in their deceitful scheming.

29:28.603 --> 29:36.754
The world is full of distractions of teaching that can take us away from Jesus, encourages to put our roots in other things

