I studied ozone when I was at university, doing my research.

29:57.702 --> 30:00.686
Chopper's fake ozone, that's ozone that's around us, that we breathe in.

30:01.787 --> 30:03.770
And it was amazing.

30:03.790 --> 30:08.136
You increased it by a little bit in the climate.

30:08.937 --> 30:09.938
It absolutely

30:10.370 --> 30:11.591
destroyed clover.

30:12.953 --> 30:16.796
Just a small change in the pollution robbed clover of its thriving.

30:19.239 --> 30:35.155
When we place ourselves in environments that are polluting our faith, when we allow weeds to grow up and kind of starve our roots of nutrients, of life, we just don't do very well.

30:35.915 --> 30:38.578
We certainly can't find fullness of life.

30:39.522 --> 30:43.367
Last year, I'm going to be honest, I didn't give my garden the attention it deserved.

30:44.388 --> 30:48.073
And so rather than growing veg, I grew weeds.

30:48.093 --> 30:49.575
And the veg just didn't like it.

30:50.136 --> 30:52.659
