31:18.855 --> 31:19.717
I'm going to pull that one.

31:19.737 --> 31:20.859
I'm going to do another one over here.

31:21.239 --> 31:22.341
I'm going to do another one over here.

31:22.361 --> 31:23.323
I'm just going to keep it nice.

31:23.383 --> 31:24.945
And that's what happens on a Sunday morning.

31:25.666 --> 31:27.149
