31:27.189 --> 31:30.354
It challenges our thinking, you know, I'm not sure I've thought of that correctly.

31:30.498 --> 31:33.683
Well, actually, I could do some prayer about this, or this is a really difficult thing.

31:34.144 --> 31:38.470
I'm not, or this is an opportunity that I don't think it's the right thing, but I'm tempted.

