32:41.658 --> 32:48.027
Gathering weekly on a Sunday is like a warm summer's day, where the clouds roll away.

32:48.067 --> 32:51.371
You know those and you go outside and you're just bathed in sunshine.

32:54.215 --> 32:59.122
That's what it's like when we come on a Sunday and we worship together and we hear the word of God.

32:59.650 --> 33:01.853
taught, and we have fellowshiped together.

33:02.333 --> 33:07.619
The clouds of life roll away, and our full attention goes on Jesus.

33:08.981 --> 33:12.044
