33:15.268 --> 33:18.692
When you have a day like that and you watch, you're gonna be, and you can almost see them grow.

33:18.712 --> 33:24.939
They really do grow in one day of warm summer day with no clouds.

33:26.501 --> 33:27.122
It's amazing.

33:28.930 --> 33:33.636
Yeah, Monday to Saturday in our lives, of course we have moments of sunshine, we do.

33:35.098 --> 33:37.041
